data.description: YES, an RV neighborhood where you can store your RV above the fence line!  This house is Beautiful and SHOWS LIKE A MODEL! Modern wood-look plank flooring, open spacious kitchen with a generous island that has cabinets on both sides! Staggered cabinets with crown molding, pendant lights and even a ''coffee corner''! A great floor plan with split owners suite, large family room/dining area and a laundry room with a doggy door built in! Private lot with no back or side neighbor as it sides common area, the mountain views are gorgeous! The 2 car garage has an access door to the side yard, added canned lights and ceiling fan! So many features in this home, don't miss this one!!
